<h1>Status</h1>

<h3>Hosting</h3>
We found a way to significantly decrease our monthly hosting cost - from almost $700/month to $150/month. This includes the total hosting for our all of our websites and customers websites. And even better, it will allow us to do a better job of offering benefits to our hosting customers. <br /><br />

We expect to complete the transition from our previous hosting solution to the new one within the next month.<br />


<h3>Marketing</h3>
Since April 30th, every weekday we have been placing entries on our blog at <a href="www.livestockofamerica.com/Blog/" class = "pressbody" target = "_blank">https://www.livestockofamerica.com/Blog/</a> and our Facebook page at<a href="https://www.facebook.com/LivestockOfAmerica/" class = "pressbody" target = "_blank">www.facebook.com/LivestockOfAmerica/</a> . 





<h3>Accelerator</h3>
We are now into the second week of the NewChip accelerator (<a href = "https://www.newchip.com" class = "pressbody" target = "_blank">www.newchip.com</a>). The first week was focused on branding. The second week, starting Wednesday, will be focused on building teams, recruiting executives, and creating a strong company culture.<br /><br />


